    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PARTY GAME COLLECTION FOR 1 TO 4 PLAYERS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy 5 fast, funny and highly replayable minigames. Play alone, gather friends on the couch, or use Remote Play Together to bring everyone online. Simple to pick up, chaotic to master, and perfect for any game night!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BURGER BLITZ</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you create the perfect burger under time pressure? Memorize the recipe and be the first to assemble your burger. Play alone or battle your friends in this battle of speed and memory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169450/extras/91fa2f3d5e1e8772deb8351978488b7a.poster.avif?t=1764312231\" width=1170 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169450/extras/91fa2f3d5e1e8772deb8351978488b7a.webm?t=1764312231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CROCODILE RIVER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cooperative rowing game where teamwork is everything. Navigate a twisting river filled with floating debris and nasty crocodiles to be the first explorer to reach the end. The farther you get, the higher your score... if your crew survives long enough. Do you dare to be an explorer?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169450/extras/d1047ba576c5807ddc84917b8703fbc4.poster.avif?t=1764312231\" width=1170 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169450/extras/d1047ba576c5807ddc84917b8703fbc4.webm?t=1764312231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BLAST ARENA</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you outsmart your opponents when danger comes from all directions? Place bombs, create chain reactions, clear the map and gather power-ups to gain the advantage. Four will enter the arena, only one will make it out alive. Will it be you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169450/extras/2194574623486ba22d37adbafcbd405e.poster.avif?t=1764312231\" width=1170 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169450/extras/2194574623486ba22d37adbafcbd405e.webm?t=1764312231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >... and 2 more mystery games! (in development - to be announced)</p>",
